    "The dataset used in the experiment was a collection of five datasets representing five undergraduate courses, each of which was hosted by the Moodle platform and lasted for one semester.",
    "Twenty distinct pairs of datasets were created by individually matching the features of associated courses.",
    "The DNN model was trained using the dataset from the first course, and after a predetermined number of epochs, it was applied to the dataset from the second course for additional training.",
    "The results showed that while the proposed strategy easily outperformed the baseline model, a fair performance was generally attained.",
    "The study by Aslam et al (2021) has examined data from two courses (mathematics and Portuguese) and included information on student's demographic, socioeconomic, educational, and course grade data."
